               </AC_QUALITY>
               <AC_PRICE>
                  <AC_WEIGHTING>15 %</AC_WEIGHTING>
               </AC_PRICE>
               <OPTIONS/>
               <OPTIONS_DESCR>
                  <P>Other Local Authorities within the Greater Manchester Combined Authority (GMCA) may be able to join the contract at a later stage. This would be subject to the availability of appropriate levels of funding and capacity to meet the requirements.</P>
               </OPTIONS_DESCR>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
